{"tid":1403885,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷一拋 前Big Four會計師:「手中鈔票亦是抗爭工具 」","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:32.000Z","uid":157404,"like":148,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"085710e8bd62e0a94a060d3c87dea5fa431b79d3","tid":1403885,"uid":157404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"「香港經濟本來就依靠金融業，及引伸出來的服務業，影響經濟就是直接影響香港的根基，後果最深遠，需要時間去修復的。就好像之前大家去提款一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果齊人做，會是一個很有效、很大影響力的行動。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n阿樹提出「三罷一拋」理論，解釋港人如何以金融手段跟政權抗爭：三罷，即謂罷工、罷市、罷買；一拋意思為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拋售港元，轉持美元外幣</span></span></strong>，「其實有兩個方向，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果一個地區的市民也不相信自己的貨幣，一定會引申連串的後果</span>，讓外界知道，這地區的人都開始不相信自己的政府，作為一個外國人如何100%信任你？」當外資撤走資金，香港經濟會直接受重創，連帶在香港有資產的政府高官和商家，也會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n阿樹認為市民最容易做到，且最能保障自己又最安全的，是兌換美金，「美元是最強勢貨幣，我們不是以投資角度去想：兌哪種貨幣會賺更多錢？而是以避過政治風險的角度去想：手持哪種貨幣最安全？」港人應理性審時度勢，香港政局動盪，誰也無法估計明天發生甚麼事，正如一個月前也想不到警方能隨意拿真槍指嚇市民。「把一部份資產兌換美金，有甚麼事最多輸十點，即是1兌1.75 與1兌1.85的分別，<span style=\"color: red;\">萬一香港維持不到聯繫匯率，港幣大幅度貶值</span>，你今天兌了美金，資產就得到保障。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190804/59890731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59890731&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvLPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=1236de66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190804%2F59890731&h=261f43ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190804/59890731</a>"},{"pid":"aeae9a746ef771a7d3f9f1d0205defa86421b341","tid":1403885,"uid":216789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，[b]"},{"pid":"48d499545cc56a612dd9e05663cb02961fae752f","tid":1403885,"uid":265092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d46da51ae326952750fbbde70375c11730e2e3","tid":1403885,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f70e321eeb780eeef2273bbf5eb497659bfa186","tid":1403885,"uid":222190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"(學術討論)如果有2百萬人同時去銀行㩒錢 會點樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ad797a701457f85e73cb3cbd4851f245dd1ecea","tid":1403885,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d308fb2bf176c560ecc01096ed56c1260f69bc4","tid":1403885,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc2481f339d915dbbacc73f73638678d1e1af18","tid":1403885,"uid":264908,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:52:24.000Z","msg":"「如果一個地區的市民也不相信自己的貨幣，一定會引申連串的後果，讓外界知道，這地區的人都開始不相信自己的政府，作為一個外國人如何100%信任你？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2583aec31135250ce31a22daa410f8e1dda368","tid":1403885,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea2ed938e2c210dc81a13f6ba27a4351a704f59","tid":1403885,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03